# UI Refinement Implementation Plan

## Goal
Make the UI more polished by fixing status bar overlap issues, setting specific page backgrounds to white, ensuring titles are always visible, and improving responsiveness.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> - Background colors for Bible, Praise, Prayer, and Memo pages will be changed from colored tints (blue-50, etc.) to **White**.
> - Sticky headers will be implemented to keep titles visible.
> - `env(safe-area-inset-top)` will be used to prevent status bar overlap.

## Proposed Changes

### Global Styles
#### [MODIFY] [index.css](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/나의 사랑하는 책/src/index.css)
- Add utility classes for safe area padding/margins if needed (e.g., `safe-pt`, `safe-top`).

### Layout & Navigation
#### [MODIFY] [Layout.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/나의 사랑하는 책/src/Layout.jsx)
- Ensure the main container respects `safe-area-inset-top` so the background extends but content doesn't overlap.
- Actually, since individual pages define their own full-height containers, I might need to move the padding logic to [Layout](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/Layout.jsx#4-27) or ensure pages handle it.
- **Decision**: Update [Layout.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/Layout.jsx) to have a top padding that respects safe area, or pass a class to children. Given the current structure where pages have `min-h-[calc(100vh-100px)]` etc., adjustments might be needed per page or centrally in Layout.

### Page Components
#### [MODIFY] [BiblePage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/나의 사랑하는 책/src/pages/BiblePage.jsx)
- Change root `bg-blue-50` to `bg-white`.
- Make the "Top Box" `sticky top-0` and add `z-50`.
- Add `padding-top: env(safe-area-inset-top)` to the sticky header to prevent it from being hidden behind the status bar.
- Adjust internal spacing/colors if needed for contrast against white.

#### [MODIFY] [PraisePage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/나의 사랑하는 책/src/pages/PraisePage.jsx)
- Change root `bg-pink-50` to `bg-white`.
- Make the Header Area `sticky top-0 z-50` with safe area padding.

#### [MODIFY] [PrayerPage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/나의 사랑하는 책/src/pages/PrayerPage.jsx)
- Change root `bg-yellow-50` to `bg-white`.
- Make the Header `sticky top-0 z-50` with safe area padding.

#### [MODIFY] [MemoPage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/나의 사랑하는 책/src/pages/MemoPage.jsx)
